### Delete Azure AI Search Index

# This tests the Azure AI Search DELETE endpoint used in src/index.ts:292

@endpoint = https://bubble-chat-ai-search-s1-2.search.windows.net

# @prompt indexName Index Name bubble-demo-example-index
# @secret apiKey Azure Search API Key

DELETE {{endpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}?api-version=2023-11-01 HTTP/1.1
Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
